"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"third_party_shipper>`, como :doc:`FedEx </applications/inventory_and_mrp/"
"inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/fedex>`, :doc:`UPS </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/ups_credentials>` ou :doc:`DHL </applications/"
"inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/"
"dhl_credentials>` para otimizar as operações de envio. Conectar-se a um "
"provedor externo permite gerar :doc:`etiquetas de rastreamento </"
"applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/"
"setup_configuration/labels>` automaticamente e oferecer aos clientes várias "
"opções de entrega no :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/checkout/steps>`."

