msgid "to configure shipping :ref:`based on rules <inventory/shipping/rules>`;"
msgstr ""
"para configurar envio :ref:`baseado em regras <inventory/shipping/rules>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:65
msgid ""
"to configure the :ref:`Click & Collect <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>` "
"option."
msgstr ""
"para configurar a opção :ref:`Click & Collect <ecommerce/shipping/instore-"
