#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:34
msgid ""
"To switch from one website's frontend to another, click the website "
"selection drop-down in the top right corner and select the website you want "
"to switch to."
msgstr ""
"Para alternar entre a interface de um site e outro, clique no menu suspenso "
